Build and installation
======================

This fork builds with a single Makefile. Autotools and build.sh are not used.

Required tools and libraries:

* GNU make
* C23-capable C compiler
* C++20-capable C++ compiler
* pkg-config
* ncursesw
* readline
* curl
* fftw3
* libmpdclient >= 2.8
* taglib C API

Build:

    make

Run tests:

    make check

Install:

    sudo make install

Install under another prefix:

    PREFIX=/opt/ncmpcpp make install

Remove build outputs:

    make clean

If the working tree still contains files from the old autotools build system
or the old shell build script, remove them with:

    make prune-autotools
